name: Theresa Cho
about: Outside of school, I enjoy watching superhero movies (The Dark Knight is amazing - change my mind) Parks and Rec & the Office, and singing. I have joined Cornell Music VS on singing trips to Cayuga Ridge, a nursing home nearby, and have participated in the mass choir on Sunday nights. I am also a big sib in Cornell Catholic and a senior consultant for CS 1110: Intro to Python!
